GS_impute_clean.Rd

Supplementary function for GSimp Multiple missing variables imputation

GS_impute_clean(
  data_miss,
  iters_each = 100,
  iters_all = 20,
  initial = "qrilc",
  lo = -Inf,
  hi = "min",
  imp_model = "glmnet_pred",
  gibbs = data.frame(row = integer(), col = integer())
)

Arguments

data_miss

data to impute

iters_each

number (100); vector of numbers, e.g. rep(100, 20)

iters_all

= 20

initial

character ('qrilc'/'lysm') initialized data matrix

lo

number; vector; functions like min/max/median/mean

hi

number; vector; functions like min/max/median/mean

imp_model

= glmnet_pred,

gibbs

= data.frame(row = integer(), col=integer())
